				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$\sim5{,}190$\end{document} images per PUC, or 15,570 total images.

The DDC will start acquiring image data just before the rover separates from the descent stage and continues acquiring data through rover touchdown on the surface. The DDC acquires data at 12 fps for ∼75\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
